ke":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T03:39:51.000Z","msg":"冇野做既搵野做,冇錢既搵錢,<br />\n呢場唔係一場定生死既戰爭<br />\n係長期,各方面既對抗<br />\n無論你自己,或者幫人,你都需要有經濟能力<br />\n大家加油"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T03:42:07.000Z","msg":"冇錯，你就算只係一星期落樓下一次更新連儂牆已經得"},{"pid":"d2266734313ddb1222ed3fc44441a8ed2d70c5ef","tid":1557024,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T03:48:03.000Z","msg":"佢地日日講大話可以冷處理"},{"pid":"529c4836881fb087c144a3d57001df85e2ddff47","tid":1557024,"uid":34239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T03:48:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97f434215589931b305283c5c4324c522c57d227","tid":1557024,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:00:18.000Z","msg":"咪再日日吹死線，現階段肯搏命嘅人根本太少，唔好再諗短期，諗長期呀"},{"pid":"10d5d1377a3235c268aa7a8accae8b5bb8546398","tid":1557024,"uid":272188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:01:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫得推上熱門</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n吾係狗 吾係香港政府 要全世界對準政權 果個人叫中共 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【海外文宣戰線】一個外國巴同我講ge野 The enemy is the communist party.<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1554741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1554741</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ae57fe2bd1f107b1aae9946f83ad90967b77c20e","tid":1557024,"uid":69761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:02:59.000Z","msg":"長期抗爭"},{"pid":"fcd7908a81b0a8e39c2e59036f05d978da4b743b","tid":1557024,"uid":204194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:04:05.000Z","msg":"消防兩次點算的傷者數目不同，到場後初步點算為 <span style=\"color: red;\">10 人</span>，最終 <span style=\"color: red;\">7 人</span>送院<br />\n<br />\n位置四：22 : 57 太子站底層月台 <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">往中環</span></strong>車廂<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">內</span></span></strong><br />\n急救期間，列車突然一搖、開出，時為 <span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>23 : 03</strong></span>分。<br />\n<br />\n位置七：<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>23 : 00 </strong></span>太子站底層月台 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>往中環</strong></span>第 5 卡至<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>車尾</strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">3 分鐘後</span></strong>，往中環列車開出；再過 2、3 分鐘往調景嶺列車亦開出，同時警方開始驅趕月台上所有記者。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>23:03 match 23:00+3mins</strong></span><br />\n<strong>所以係有可能有人見到，係22:57 - 23:03 之間，共6分鐘</strong><br />\n<br />\n位置六：23 : 07 太子站底層月台 <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">往中環</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">車頭</span></span></strong>對出<br />\n他記得被捕者一排排地蹲下，堆了至少三排、近 60 人；然後左方有一位昏迷不醒的黑衣男子，驟眼看沒有血，不知如何弄成這樣。有一個軍綠色 T 恤的男子則被打得頭破血流，還有一個「肥仔」好像恐慌症發作，一度手腳僵直呼吸困難。 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">共三人</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「你問我覺得有無死人？我不能排除這個可能。」David說，「因為我親眼見過有人不省人事，連同那軍綠色衫的男仔，事後在警署都沒碰過面了。」</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n剩下的事情，只有警方、港鐵職員、消防救護員及被捕者知道。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1556113/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1556113/page/1</a><br />\n【專題】地圖重組 8.31太子站 閉路電視有真相嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%B0%88%E9%A1%8C-%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%96%E9%87%8D%E7%B5%84-8-31%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%AB%99-%E9%96%89%E8%B7%AF%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%E6%9C%89%E7%9C%9F%E7%9B%B8%E5%97%8E/?fbclid=IwAR22jHiXy_7IgLQgLUR96edc3INp30gBuPOQSUGxaXbhPI-J2L5fwjD_Xds\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25B0%2588%25E9%25A1%258C-%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%259C%2596%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%25B5%2584-8-31%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%25AB%2599-%25E9%2596%2589%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A6%2596%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%259C%259F%25E7%259B%25B8%25E5%2597%258E%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR22jHiXy_7IgLQgLUR96edc3INp30gBuPOQSUGxaXbhPI-J2L5fwjD_Xds&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdD5zZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=a42954b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25B0%2588%25E9%25A1%258C-%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%259C%2596%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%25B5%2584-8-31%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%25AB%2599-%25E9%2596%2589%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A6%2596%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%259C%259F%25E7%259B%25B8%25E5%2597%258E%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR22jHiXy_7IgLQgLUR96edc3INp30gBuPOQSUGxaXbhPI-J2L5fwjD_Xds&h=72fdfbfc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%B0%88%E9%A1%8C-%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%96%E9%87%8D%E7%B5%84-8-31%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%AB%99-%E9%96%89%E8%B7%AF%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%E6%9C%89%E7%9C%9F%E7%9B%B8%E5%97%8E/?fbclid=IwAR22jHiXy_7IgLQgLUR96edc3INp30gBuPOQSUGxaXbhPI-J2L5fwjD_Xds</a><br />\n<br />\n立埸新聞為香港人尋求831真相，極重要，請睇！<br />\n<br />\n太子站重要，新屋嶺一樣重要！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1554008/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1554008/page/1</a><br />\nWhy not both"},{"pid":"130f3ab5784fd512448fc7519fa9abac43bf9cdc","tid":1557024,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:04:15.000Z","msg":"今日個聯個記者會又係好怪<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">其實係真係假佢都冇需要攪咁大場戲，佢地一定係有其他目的</span>"},{"pid":"be3fe7ef286e22c765138d068892aa0a445ac1da","tid":1557024,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba177899e6669e723db38ce5bbd4dd8716446481","tid":1557024,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T03:17:13.000Z","msg":"跪求大家坐噃低諗清楚先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:05:44.000Z","msg":"提供小小方向<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532845\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\"